      "writtenOn": "2017-04-27T17:04:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Sure, but even a few more characters like \u0027Cr/An\u0027 brings the ellipsis which makes it unreadable. So I see no other option other than combining unless you have a better naming suggestion. Also this list will likely continue to grow so we will need some way to compress it.",
